  <summary>10/2/1998--Introduced.
Amends part A (Temporary Assistance for Needy Families) (TANF) of title IV of the Social Security Act to make any State with an increase in child poverty of five percent or more in a fiscal year ineligible for a high performance bonus for the next fiscal year.</summary>
